* Electronics Technicians Association (ETA)<br>
* Government Electronics & Information Technology Association<br>
* Industrial Designers Society of America (IDSA)
* International Association of Electronics Recyclers<br>
* International Auto Sound Challenge Association<br>
* International Electronics Manufacturers & Consumers of America<br>
* International Housewares Association<br>
